==English==

===Noun===
'''plumbism'''
# {{medicine}} A diseased condition, produced by the [[absorption]] of [[lead]], common among workers in this metal or in its compounds, as among [[painter]]s, [[typesetter]]s, etc. It is characterized by various symptoms, as [[lead colic]], [[lead line]], and [[wrist drop]].

